{"tid":539663,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"違泊拖車","createTime":"2018-01-24T18:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T10:16:37.000Z","uid":118158,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1955a06c06ae55c39bd18a93593d32347b6c30a4","tid":539663,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:04:33.000Z","msg":"小弟都知違泊唔岩亦唔應該，貪方便24/1泊左架車係堅拿道東鵝頸橋底路肩位（位置一定無阻塞道路）。<br />\n<br />\n12點3左右泊低，5點半諗住拎車就發現點解個位變左架貨van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 橋底近油站一向都有鐵馬駐守。去問下啦，佢叫我打上999問睇下係咪拖走左。<br />\n<br />\n之後999再比扣留中心電話我話拖走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當堂個人都定d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但泊街唔係阻街塞死先會拖架咩？同埋我泊街都會驚阻到人上落貨都會留電話。拖之前唔係都會打電話架咩？<br />\n<br />\nChing 有無經驗？我知錯亦唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038d9381155513b765a127d09bcf0dfc375211e4","tid":539663,"uid":116530,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf066fb522ae94ba608ec52a97025a87db376c","tid":539663,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"有人瘋狂投訴話知你泊巷尾總之唔泊得就可以拖架啦"},{"pid":"e5dcbbb4f3693f2e24b41c8d2750b92c9c49a744","tid":539663,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"共其實拖完點拎返?<br />\n要唔要比錢同驗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419647d03f86d044a3ecd7acbc477a0fc1e43065","tid":539663,"uid":118158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5dcbbb4f3693f2e24b41c8d2750b92c9c49a744","tid":539663,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:11:40.000Z","msg":"共其實拖完點拎返?<br />\n要唔要比錢同驗車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"$560好似頭兩日基本收拖車費，之後日子唔清楚。<br />\n未計當中有無其他牛肉乾<br />\n<br />\n好似改裝車拖走又另一玩法"},{"pid":"b2719a3280ddea215b669dea5c2596f3ded06d02","tid":539663,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10cf066fb522ae94ba608ec52a97025a87db376c","tid":539663,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"有人瘋狂投訴話知你泊巷尾總之唔泊得就可以拖架啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"奇怪點解無打電話黎叫我走話我阻住姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdf13209357761c861538a829854ac5b32772b9","tid":539663,"uid":131241,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b2719a3280ddea215b669dea5c2596f3ded06d02","tid":539663,"uid":118158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10cf066fb522ae94ba608ec52a97025a87db376c","tid":539663,"uid":158755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"有人瘋狂投訴話知你泊巷尾總之唔泊得就可以拖架啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"奇怪點解無打電話黎叫我走話我阻住姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T19:47:21.000Z","msg":"老馮打比你咩"},{"pid":"c17cc97066b788d0d4a169792785cb46e6b04c20","tid":539663,"uid":147380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T21:12:42.000Z","msg":"佢想睇你仆街又點會打比你"},{"pid":"a83982e991c58390acfb804a4f60142d9ba53687","tid":539663,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"無法, 你重要泊咁多個鐘, 個個位會唔會係人地鋪頭上落貨位"},{"pid":"69f503eb6a67c2f4464b8e0da0145b0e5544cac6","tid":539663,"uid":50101,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"12點擺到5點係講緊中午？你都算威啦，日光日白銅鑼灣鬧市咁樣一鳩泊底走咗去，你係新手車主？其實你聽邊個講話塞住人哋轉彎先拖？一般投訴PC仔嚟到係費撚事煩先打電話叫你揸走咋，白炸行過見到就唔係咁講法，再講咩唔阻人都係你自己認為，求其有個垃圾婆話你阻住推木頭車已經可以勾鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28a36cd9b9685ca80a0eb7c39f88f8ba609b270","tid":539663,"uid":10398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:46:39.000Z","msg":"泊一個鐘都驚啦下嘛 你泊成日都夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e147bfc142ba34bc0cb53dfebb9ee82dc9759c45","tid":539663,"uid":13875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"你同有單新聞比行李費包搬上的士嗰老女人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c026aaea63318fd76f3b36fbb920d71405668e2c","tid":539663,"uid":45672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:49:08.000Z","msg":"旺位泊一個鐘都怕。 你泊半日仲好意思講。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d70c5079401f9b27e63fda8a23be92ee74a755","tid":539663,"uid":9838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"dde119e68b94039b8ab046790f400fc87227fe25","tid":539663,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"如果多啲拖車就好，霸晒條路其他車唔晒行咩"},{"pid":"6308e5d5c06f498a2d6cdb56d574d6d1f7f47e5f","tid":539663,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dde119e68b94039b8ab046790f400fc87227fe25","tid":539663,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"如果多啲拖車就好，霸晒條路其他車唔晒行咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"特別係旺區, 就算唔阻路, 車夠過, 但係都會引起塞車"},{"pid":"073f