if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心泊咁耐就入車場啦<br />\n抵你比人拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fb253a4d0ec615c36c29bee06c2ca58182826f","tid":539663,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:14:07.000Z","msg":"可能有工程要進行<br />\n你坐住左D野"},{"pid":"073cad60aba0289070cec21597b24159e3795226","tid":539663,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"無擺電話？<br />\n差佬都會打比你啦"},{"pid":"ad81e273b792cf59bb2c60e7568e40a8861c8207","tid":539663,"uid":13416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"其實呀Sir係咪睇心情先會打黎<br />\n未試過拖走<br />\n之前仲試過有一次打俾我叫我揸走部車唔抄我"},{"pid":"abfd9965b1f7ed04828de0c5d129a66caf089304","tid":539663,"uid":131241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad81e273b792cf59bb2c60e7568e40a8861c8207","tid":539663,"uid":13416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"其實呀Sir係咪睇心情先會打黎<br />\n未試過拖走<br />\n之前仲試過有一次打俾我叫我揸走部車唔抄我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T22:46:59.000Z","msg":"有人投訴落去趕車先有機會打，因為佢抄一張番到去要做多好多野，有張form要逐張逐張填<br />\n咖啡仔/阿sir睇住做功課or果日個operation係要抄夠幾多張就就多數唔打"},{"pid":"596fbe49c9144bd563012352f96a5b43a13d1efc","tid":539663,"uid":24989,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T22:57:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n時代廣場、利舞臺附近有咁撚多停車場你唔泊，你泊街邊泊半日？<br />\n<br />\n抵你死啦"}]}